  "Description": "The TPRT9013 is a high-performance, 500mA low-dropout linear voltage regulator designed for space-constrained portable and RF/wireless applications. It features an extremely high power supply rejection ratio (PSRR) and ultra-low dropout voltage, ensuring stable output voltage even with a small difference between input and output. The device includes an enable (CE) pin for shutdown control to minimize power consumption and is available in fixed output voltage variants within a compact SOT23-5 package.",
